<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/chris-grigg> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Chris Grigg is Chair of the National Wealth Fund and of Evelyn Partners, the wealth management company. He was also appointed non-executive Chair for Melrose plc, the aerospace company, in March 2025. In his executive career, Chris was most recently CEO of British Land. Before that, he was CEO of Barclays Commercial Bank. Chris’s earlier career was spent at Goldman Sachs, where he was a Partner, and at Morgan Grenfell. Chris has an MA in Economics from the University of Cambridge."@en .
